6. The computer-implemented method of claim 1, wherein receiving the media feed comprises:
accessing at least one of a capture device, a capture file, and a network resource;
receiving data from at least one of the capture device, the capture file, and the network resource;
populating one or more buffers with the received data; and
creating the media feed with the received data in the buffers, wherein the media feed includes one or more media frames for the received data in the buffers.

18. The system of claim 13, wherein receiving the media feed comprises:
accessing at least one of a capture device, a capture file, and a network resource;
receiving data from at least one of the capture device, the capture file, and the network resource;
populating one or more buffers with the received data; and
creating the media feed with the received data in the buffers, wherein the media feed includes one or more media frames for the received data in the buffers.
